{
  "stem": "8527.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She is now deceased.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They escaped to Russia in 1939 when the Russians were retreating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Germans and the-- and the Russians were at the-- they were there in the same time in our town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When they were retreating, a lot the-- a lot of the Jews, quite a few Jews escaped to Russia because they anticipated what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But a lot of people didn't believe it, especially people who had businesses and had homes, and they just didn't feel that they should be leaving that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my parents apparently decided to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, 1939, our business still continued.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Slightly, slowly, things started happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews had to start wearing armbands, and there were rations to start with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the people were gathered from the outskirts of the city and brought into the town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A certain part of the town was allocated towards a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then about 1940, they started putting walls around the ghetto at the main entrances and on the streets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the fields, there was barbed wire with guards walking around it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was extremely mature, I don't know why, at a very young age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll-- I'll touch on it in a-- in a second.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just want to tell you about the-- the commerce that was going on while the ghetto-- while in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember they used to smuggle beef in through the barbed wire by cutting the fences.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, as a kid, there were two, three people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would slaughter a cow in a barn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, there was meat for people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had-- we had food to eat-- to eat during those times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never felt any-- any-- I didn't feel any problems.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
